{"id":"api/core/BootstrapOptions","title":"BootstrapOptions","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/BootstrapOptions\", \"name\": \"BootstrapOptions\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/application/application_ref.ts#L88-L146\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"bootstrapoptions\">BootstrapOptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions#bootstrapoptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"culhhzk2nlc0zp78n1120o3nl\">为引导过程提供其他选项。</p>\n\n  </section><section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">BootstrapOptions</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZone\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZone</span>?: NgZone | 'zone.js' | 'noop'</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZoneEventCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZoneEventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZoneRunCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZoneRunCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n\n</section>\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a id=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ngZone\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZone</span>?: <a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a> | 'zone.js' | 'noop'</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dop85bz5y7jnlrf7bo5woq1hl\">（可选）指定应该使用哪个 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code>。</p>\n          <ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6dp116msgb4nn6rtuser49ogk\">提供你自己的 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code> 实例。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"95vlnjrpirpo3bewvumw7skb5\"><code>zone.js</code> - 使用需要 <code>Zone.js</code> <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5dy0r3ue6s5d79kt9f1vah29p\"><code>noop</code> - 使用什么都不做的 <code>NoopNgZone</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ngZoneEventCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZoneEventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"esm6cbgiipquc96c0k267fuje\">（可选）指定或不指定合并事件变更检测。考虑以下情况。</p>\n          <code-example>\n&lt;div (click)=\"doSomething()\"&gt;\n  &lt;button (click)=\"doSomethingElse()\"&gt;&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1esyzsczi1ptbepxoj3p0lgvg\">单击按钮时，由于事件冒泡，将调用两个事件处理程序，并触发 2 次变更检测。我们可以合并此类事件以仅触发变更检测一次。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"opuxkb1tam7k3oo5xjsad5su\">默认情况下，此选项将是 false。因此，事件将不会被合并，并且变更检测将被触发多次。如果此选项设置为 true，则变更检测将通过调度动画帧来异步触发。因此在上面的情况下，变更检测将只会触发一次。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ngZoneRunCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">ngZoneRunCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9t3bps9m3r3ahpih477shlszu\">（可选）指定 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a>#run()</code> 方法调用是否应合并为单个变更检测。</p>\n          <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"czk3su6u1np51ws2huk6ihka0\">考虑以下情况。</p>\n<code-example>\nfor (let i = 0; i &lt; 10; i ++) {\n  ngZone.run(() =&gt; {\n    // do something\n  });\n}\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1vof025w3hjhzx8xsfhd8810d\">这种情况会多次触发变更检测。使用 ngZoneRunCoalescing 选项，事件循环中的所有变更检测只会触发一次。此外，变更检测是在 requestAnimation 中执行的。</p>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/PlatformRef\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\n - errors/NG5000\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions#bootstrapoptions\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions#instance-properties\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZone\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZoneEventCoalescing\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions#ngZoneRunCoalescing\n - api/core/NgZone\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/application/application_ref.ts#L88-L146\n-->"}